\c 23
\s Umthwalo weTire
\p
\v 1 Umthwalo\x + 13.1.\x* weTire\x + Jer. 25.22. 27.3. 47.4. Hez. 26.2. 28.26. 29.18,20. Amos 1.9. Jow. 3.4. Zek. 9.2-4.\x*. Qhinqani isililo\x + 23.14. 1 Kho. 10.22.\x*, mikhumbi yeTarshishi, ngoba ichithiwe, ukuze kungabi lendlu\x + 24.10. 7.8.\x*, ukuthi kungabi lokungena\x + 24.10. 7.8.\x*. Kuvela elizweni leKitimi\x + 23.12.\x* kwembuliwe kubo.
\v 2 Thulani\x + Jer. 47.6.\x*, bahlali besihlenge\x + 23.6.\x*; wena abakugcwalisileyo abathengiselani beSidoni\x + Josh. 19.28.\x* abachapha ulwandle.
\v 3 Langamanzi amakhulu, inzalo yeShihori\x + 1 Lan. 13.5.\x*, isivuno somfula yinzuzo yayo; njalo iyindawo yezizwe yokuthengiselana\x + Hez. 27.3.\x*.
\v 4 Woba lenhloni, Sidoni\x + Josh. 19.28.\x*; ngoba ulwandle lukhulumile, amandla olwandle, lusithi: Kangihelelwa, kangibelethanga, kangikhulisanga\x + 1.2.\x* amajaha, kangondlanga izintombi ezimsulwa\x + 1.2.\x*.
\v 5 Njengasembikweni ngeGibhithe bazahelelwa ngombiko weTire.
\v 6 Chaphelani eTarshishi\x + 23.14. 1 Kho. 10.22.\x*, qhinqani isililo, bahlali besihlenge\x + 23.6.\x*.
\v 7 Yiwo lo yini \add umuzi\add* wenu ojabulayo\x + 22.2.\x*, obudala bawo busukela ensukwini zendulo\x + Hlab. 44.1.\x*? Inyawo zawo zizawuthwalela khatshana uku\add ya\add*hlala njengowezizwe.
\v 8 Ngubani oweluleke lokhu ngeTire, omethesi womqhele, obathengisi\x + 23.11.\x* bayo bayiziphathamandla, obathengiselani bayo ngabadumileyo emhlabeni?
\v 9 IN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla ikucebisile lokhu, ukonakalisa ukuzigqaja kodumo\x + 4.2.\x* lonke, ukwenza badeleleke\x + 9. 1.\x* bonke abadumileyo bomhlaba.
\v 10 Dabula ilizwe lakho njengomfula\x + 23.3. Gen. 41.1-3.\x*, ndodakazi yeTarshishi\x + 23.14. 1 Kho. 10.22.\x*; akuselamandla\x + Jobe 12.21.\x*.
\v 11 Yelulele isandla sayo phezu kolwandle, inyikinye imibuso\x + 14.16.\x*; iN\nd kosi\nd* ilayezile imelene leKhanani, ukuchitha inqaba zayo.
\v 12 Yasisithi: Kawusayikuphinda ujabule, ntombi emsulwa ecindezelweyo, ndodakazi yeSidoni; eKhithimu\x + 23.12.\x* sukuma uchaphe; lakhona kakuyikuba lokuphumula kuwe.
\v 13 Khangela ilizwe lamaKhaladiya\x + 13.19. 43.14. 47.1,5. 48.14,20. 2 Kho. 25.4. Gen. 22.22.\x*; lesisizwe sasingekho; amaSiriya asisekelela bona abahlala enkangala\x + Hlab. 72.9. 74.14.\x*; amisa imiphotshongo yawo yokuvimbezela\x + Jer. 6.27.\x*, abhidliza izigodlo zalo; alenza laba lunxiwa\x + 25.2.\x*.
\v 14 Qhinqani isililo, mikhumbi yeTarshishi\x + 23.14. 1 Kho. 10.22.\x*, ngoba inqaba yenu ichithekile.
\p
\v 15 Kuzakuthi-ke ngalolosuku iTire ikhohlakale okweminyaka engamatshumi ayisikhombisa\x + Jer. 25.9-11. 27.3-6.\x*, njengokwensuku zenkosi eyodwa\x + Dan. 8.20.\x*. Ekupheleni kweminyaka engamatshumi ayisikhombisa\x + 23.17.\x* kuzakuba khona eTire okunjengengoma yewule\x + 23.17.\x*.
\v 16 Thatha ichacho\x + 21.5.\x*, ubhode umuzi, wule elikhohlakeleyo, utshaye kamnandi\x + Hlab. 33.3.\x*, uhlabele ingoma ezinengi, ukuze ukhunjulwe.
\p
\v 17 Kuzakuthi-ke ekupheleni kweminyaka engamatshumi ayisikhombisa\x + 23.17.\x* iN\nd kosi\nd* iyihambele iTire\x + 24.21.\x*; njalo izabuyela ekuqhatshweni\x + 23.17.\x* kobuwule bayo; izawula\x + Isam. 17.2. 18.3,9.\x* layo yonke imibuso yomhlaba phezu kobuso bomhlaba.
\v 18 Lokuthengiselana kwayo lokuqhatshwa kwayo kuzakuba yibungcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 14.20.\x*; kakuyikulondolozwa kumbe kubuthelelwe, ngoba inzuzo yayo yokuthengiselana izakuba ngeyabahlala phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Hlab. 45.12. Ezra 3.7. Hlab. 87.4. Hez. 28.24. Seb. 21.3,4.\x*, ukuze badle basuthe\x + 55.2. Hez. 39.19. Hag. 1.6.\x*, babe lezigqoko ezinhle.